 | `BREAK_BETWEEN_ITERATIONS`   | `600`             | Thermal equilibration wait Phase 1 → 2 (s)                       |
 | `RETRY_BACKOFF_MULTIPLIER`   | `2.0`             | Retry wait exponential multiplier                                |
 | `RETRY_BACKOFF_CAP_S`        | `1800`            | Retry wait upper cap (s)                                         |
 
+Residual backend switch (optional):
+- `TPS_RESIDUAL_BACKEND=auto|cpp|numpy` (default: `auto`)
+- `auto` uses `tps_engine` when importable, otherwise keeps NumPy path.
+
+When using C++ backend from `tps-hpc-engine`:
+```bash
+# Example: if tps-hpc-engine is a sibling directory
+export PYTHONPATH="../tps-hpc-engine/build:$PYTHONPATH"
+export TPS_RESIDUAL_BACKEND=auto
+```
+
 > **Same-machine deployment**: Set `CLIENT_PATH_TO_RESULT_FILE` and `SERVER_PATH` to the same Windows directory (e.g. `C:\HDResults\`). No network share required.
